name: Watched College Football, Season 2017 - Virginia at Miami
College Football, Season 2017 - Virginia at Miami

item.value: College Football, Season 2017 - Virginia at Miami

content.html:
The 6-4 Cavaliers head south to Hard Rock Stadium to battle the undefeated 9-0 Hurricanes. Miami comes off its biggest win of the season, a 41-8 triumph over then-No. 3 Notre Dame. Virginia aims to avoid a third-straight loss against the Hurricanes.

Watched on Living Room
